{"tid":1317493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家 真係要跟貼啲俾人插眼嗰位義士既情況","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T01:30:10.000Z","uid":183204,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bba24c33694daf90d39dde72cf206cd44266cb69","tid":1317493,"uid":183204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:57:30.000Z","msg":"香港大學畢業生被控非法集結<br />\n<br />\n【學苑即時】據悉一名香港大學畢業生被捕，據悉被捕時曾被警方挖眼。本刊記者其後向香港大學學生會署理會長黃程鋒查詢。黃指該名男子為香港大學的畢業生，亦為李兆基堂前堂友，目前該名男子身處於葵涌警署，已有律師到場協助，該名男子目前被控非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：連登討論區）<br />\n<br />\n新聞連結：<a href=\"https://www.undergrad.hk/17638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undergrad.hk%2F17638&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=fe339fd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.undergrad.hk/17638</a>"},{"pid":"26cbb10d255a73d3339d28ad873029cc53a9592d","tid":1317493,"uid":258711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02d3ada41c07cb7d62792dc572b769befa7134ba","tid":1317493,"uid":183204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:04:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"980ca61f569628445ba52785d92a2ee879e2bdc4","tid":1317493,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:04:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d56a918be8e95c8aab4e6bd21c05836ec01dbfd","tid":1317493,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:05:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"522b8f4ef23a023db3cb9f2c7ce408fcc07cb7d3","tid":1317493,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:05:40.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6187bd713a3fad6686da00710eb63149f85edd4a","tid":1317493,"uid":252854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"推 希望唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd131fc1764ff718bc69a2d5b7f71ed9c02b994f","tid":1317493,"uid":14